HB 934 Original 2026 Regular Session Ventrella
Abstract: Permits the possession of certain native wildlife and provides for restrictions.
Proposed law provides for possession of hand caught native wildlife with the limit of six in
a household.
Proposed law establishes requirements for pens and for not transporting the animals outside
of La.
Proposed law requires that animals be kept in appropriate enclosures.
Proposed law provides that no native wildlife may be kept in inhumane or unhealthy
conditions.
(Adds R.S. 56:129)
